content: I really like it here. It's great to date. Later, everyone will ride a bike.
It was great to take a walk with the kids!
Good place to walk and camp ^^
Sorae Ecological Wetland Park is also famous as a filming location for dramas!! If you walk, peace will come and heal. Be sure to visit it~^^
Beautiful looking Hanok style buildings as we had a good stroll along Anguk-dong area. They are actually a residential area.
cafe onion Anguk Just near Exit 3 of Anguo Station, don't miss everyone who likes to experience coffee and dessert in Hanok! You can also go shopping in Insadong and Sanqingdong.
